calcPositions

protected void calcPositions()
Calculates the points used to draw the shape. To adjust the shape of the arrow (narrower, wider, etc.), adjust the length in different placements.

drawIcon

public void drawIcon(java.awt.geom.Point2D s,
                     java.awt.geom.Point2D t)
Draws the icon. The icon is aways drawn at the target point. To change the orientation, swap the points in how the constructor and this method are called.
